OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells in the
OL,7,Fevening. Staying dry in the east
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells. Turning
OL,9,Fcloudier in the west overnight, with a
OL,10,Ffew light showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright spells and variable
OL,13,Fcloud with the odd light shower in the
OL,14,Fmorning. Drier for a time around the
OL,15,Fmiddle of the day before rain spreads
OL,16,Feast from late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
